game.name: Spinoider
game.description: Spinoider is a arcade game that requires focus, concentration and precise timing. Practice your reaction speed in this dynamic game. Avoid the red obstacles and get the highest score! You have 10 lives. The speed of the game will gradually increase. The game contains both single player and multiplayer modes. Single Player mode allows you to practice and improve your reaction speed. Try to get as much points as possible. Multiplayer mode offers the option to play in real time with someone who is online. You can play with your friends or random players. This makes the game so much more fun! The goal is to survive as long as possible. Practice in single player mode and hone your skills.
